content: Very fun to use as an adult and good for focus for each finger

This app teaches how touch typing really well. It also calculates speed & accuracy. It allows to compete with others in the house to give us incentive to improve. The audio & visuals in the app are very thoughtful, enjoyable & superb just like the rest of the App. Both the free & paid versions are superb for adults or kids learning touch typing as beginners or advanced typists improving speed. So far I haven't seen numbers row typing yet; but still the App is superb - I recommend this for all
Its helping me lern to typing it has one level tho thats harder then the level above it but so far no glitches and its a pretty good app!You can also change the languege.

I first installed the "Lite" version for my 6-year old daughter to learn typing for the very first time and the outcome was very very impressive after some few days of practice between 30 to 60 minutes in a day. Getting the full version will surely fine tune her typing skills at her age. She also loves to see her score at the end of each lesson, it motivates her to do better next time. Thanks very much Corentine for this great App!
